          <p>Treatment spray for ingrown hairs and body acne with salicylic acid.</p>
          <ul class="product-features">
            <li>Salicylic & lactic acid</li>
            <li>Antimicrobial properties</li>
            <li>Reduces inflammation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card animate-on-scroll scale-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg width="50" height="50" viewBox="0 0 50 50" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
